,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649fa251d2e324df8a827a6c2c6025b038b9eaaa","tid":586321,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71005df63fb5e8fbddb36bba2399f9e1ddda332","tid":586321,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c69a51144efe66b73bd86f9805953b26b633a3a3","tid":586321,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"泛民打手未來撚啊廢陣間就會入嚟宣布樓主係我分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意幫我出個po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"咩post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝賀保釣勇士成功登島<br />\n嚴正要求日本政府立即放人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/221202_40486471756027f70eeff827181ea44a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F221202_40486471756027f70eeff827181ea44a.jpg&h=f48ebc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/221203_674f35fc5440ce3d2849c2194ba2f2b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F221203_674f35fc5440ce3d2849c2194ba2f2b2.jpg&h=909b3697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員今天上午到日本駐港總領事館抗議，嚴正要求日本政府無條件釋放保釣成員。民主黨同時向日本駐港總領事館人員遞交抗議信，並於現場滾動雞蛋，寓意要日本滾出釣魚台。  <br />\n<br />\n以下是是次行動的相片及新聞稿  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝賀保釣勇士成功登島 嚴正要求日本政府立即放人</span></ins></strong><br />\n昨天，本港保釣船啟豐二號在在釣魚台搶灘，八名船員落水登島，豎立國旗及唱國歌，成功宣示主權，全球中國人對此深受鼓舞。 然而，我們同時亦相當擔心保釣人士的安全，據了解，登島期間，啟豐二號已多次被日本海上保安廳巡邏艇攔截，先後發射水炮及用船身撞擊，船隻嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n登島後，船員亦被拘留。對於船員的安全，民主黨極度關注。 釣魚台是中國的領土，日方無理攔截船隻登島和拘留船員，行為野蠻，我們極為憤怒，民主黨於今日早上，到日本駐港總領事館抗議，嚴正要求日方立即無條件釋放所有船員，並且對侵佔釣魚台的行為深切道歉。  <br />\n<br />\n發言人︰ 單仲偕先生(民主黨副主席) 涂謹申議員(民主黨立法會議員)<br />\n<br />\n2012年8月16日  <br />\n來源：[url]<a href=\"http://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=news/news/detail&amp;id=1222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dnews%2Fnews%2Fdetail%26id%3D1222&d=kdeg%2BZRbvRkuR6gPxUTO0sPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5c3992c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=news/news/detail&amp;id=1222</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">延伸閱讀：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[舊聞重溫] 民主派堅持反台獨免予人口實</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>司徒華主動向教育局建議，普通話進入香港教育</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新民主同盟：支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額，不應視新來港人士為掠奪資源</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>泛民：認同居港一年即享綜援，支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主黨的基本信念：我們支持香港回歸中國</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>教協葉建源：浸大生粗魯無禮不能接受，要求嚴肅處理</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>葉建源憂代繳考試費吸非學生市民報考<br />\n內地生踴躍報考DSE惹關注　葉建源：籲家長毋須過慮</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/584940/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/584940/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【蔡若蓮喪子】 前對手葉建源感難過 斥涼薄言論對死者不尊重</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/391149/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/391149/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"65587ec4c5a565e76fd0dd222e35146ca3130665","tid":586321,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aae21a58a920e6d3f897a95a5bc62e608e5acee","tid":586321,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"649fa251d2e324df8a827a6c2c6025b038b9eaaa","tid":586321,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71005df63fb5e8fbddb36bba2399f9e1ddda332","tid":586321,"uid":72730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"巴打介唔介意幫我出個po <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"咩post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝賀保釣勇士成功登島<br />\n嚴正要求日本政府立即放人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/221202_40486471756027f70eeff827181ea44a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F221202_40486471756027f70eeff827181ea44a.jpg&h=f48ebc68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/221203_674f35fc5440ce3d2849c2194ba2f2b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F221203_674f35fc5440ce3d2849c2194ba2f2b2.jpg&h=909b3697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員今天上午到日本駐港總領事館抗議，嚴正要求日本政府無條件釋放保釣成員。民主黨同時向日本駐港總領事館人員遞交抗議信，並於現場滾動雞蛋，寓意要日本滾出釣魚台。  <br />\n<br />\n以下是是次行動的相片及新聞稿  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝賀保釣勇士成功登島 嚴正要求日本政府立即放人</span></ins></strong><br />\n昨天，本港保釣船啟豐二號在在釣魚台搶灘，八名船員落水登島，豎立國旗及唱國歌，成功宣示主權，全球中國人對此深受鼓舞。 然而，我們同時亦相當擔心保釣人士的安全，據了解，登島期間，啟豐二號已多次被日本海上保安廳巡邏艇攔截，先後發射水炮及用船身撞擊，船隻嚴重損毀。<br />\n<br />\n登島後，船員亦被拘留。對於船員的安全，民主黨極度關注。 釣魚台是中國的領土，日方無理攔截船隻登島和拘留船員，行為野蠻，我們極為憤怒，民主黨於今日早上，到日本駐港總領事館抗議，嚴正要求日方立即無條件釋放所有船員，並且對侵佔釣魚台的行為深切道歉。  <br />\n<br />\n發言人︰ 單仲偕先生(民主黨副主席) 涂謹申議員(民主黨立法會議員)<br />\n<br />\n2012年8月16日  <br />\n來源：[url]<a href=\"http://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=news/news/detail&amp;id=1222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dphk.org%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dnews%2Fnews%2Fdetail%26id%3D1222&d=kdeg%2BZRbvRkuR6gPxUTO0sPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5c3992c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.dphk.org/index.php?route=news/news/detail&amp;id=1222</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">延伸閱讀：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[舊聞重溫] 民主派堅持反台獨免予人口實</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586281/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>司徒華主動向教育局建議，普通話進入香港教育</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586442/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>新民主同盟：支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額，不應視新來港人士為掠奪資源</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586422/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>泛民：認同居港一年即享綜援，支持維持家庭團聚單程証配額</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586321/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主黨的基本信念：我們支持香港回歸中國</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586292/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>教協葉建源：浸大生粗魯無禮不能接受，要求嚴肅處理</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/586459/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>葉建源憂代繳考試費吸非學生市民報考<br />\n內地生踴躍報考DSE惹關注　葉建源：籲家長毋須過慮</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/576668/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/584940/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https